<br>
IMO, we can all learn something from the philosophies of Eastern religions, but as for truly following them... hey, not everyone <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>wants</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to give up their hopes and dreams! Can you seriously imagine some of the athiests on this board voluntarily giving up self-assertion??? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
